      "widgets_values": [
        "# FreeFuse SDXL — Model & LoRA Download Guide\n# FreeFuse SDXL — 模型与LoRA下载指南\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Required Models / 所需模型\n\n### 📂 checkpoints/\n• sd_xl_base_1.0.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0/resolve/main/sd_xl_base_1.0.safetensors?download=true\n  EN: SDXL Base 1.0 checkpoint (includes UNet + CLIP + VAE)\n  中: SDXL Base 1.0 检查点模型（包含UNet + CLIP + VAE）\n\n### 📂 vae/ (Optional / 可选)\n• Built-in VAE from checkpoint is used by default\n  默认使用检查点自带的VAE\n• No separate VAE file required for SDXL\n  SDXL不需要单独的VAE文件\n\n### 📂 loras/ (LoRA Files)\n• harry_potter_xl.safetensors\n  EN: SDXL LoRA for Harry Potter (custom trained)\n  中: Harry Potter角色的SDXL LoRA（自训练）\n• daiyu_lin_xl.safetensors\n  EN: SDXL LoRA for Daiyu Lin (custom trained)\n  中: 林黛玉角色的SDXL LoRA（自训练）\n\n⚠ SDXL LoRAs must be trained for SDXL architecture.\nFlux LoRAs are NOT compatible with SDXL!\n⚠ SDXL LoRA必须基于SDXL架构训练，\nFlux LoRA与SDXL不兼容！\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Directory Structure / 目录结构\n📂 ComfyUI/models/\n├─ checkpoints/\n│  └─ sd_xl_base_1.0.safetensors\n└─ loras/\n   ├─ harry_potter_xl.safetensors\n   └─ daiyu_lin_xl.safetensors\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Important Notes / 重要提示\n• SDXL requires ~8GB VRAM for 1024×1024\n  SDXL生成1024×1024约需8GB显存\n• Uses standard CFG (7.0 recommended)\n  使用标准CFG引导（推荐7.0）\n• 30 steps recommended / 推荐30步\n• Uses CLIPTextEncode (not CLIPTextEncodeFlux)\n  使用CLIPTextEncode（非CLIPTextEncodeFlux）\n• Supports negative prompts / 支持负面提示词\n• SDXL concept_text should be shorter than Flux\n  SDXL的concept_text应比Flux更简短"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
