        "# FreeFuse SDXL — Complete Parameter Guide\n# FreeFuse SDXL — 完整参数指南\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Workflow Overview / 工作流概览\nEN: FreeFuse uses a two-phase approach for multi-LoRA composition:\n  Phase 1: Collect cross-attention → generate spatial masks\n  Phase 2: Apply masks to LoRAs → full denoising generation\n中: FreeFuse 采用两阶段方法实现多LoRA合成：\n  阶段1：收集交叉注意力 → 生成空间掩码\n  阶段2：对LoRA应用掩码 → 完整去噪生成\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 1. LoRA Loader / LoRA加载器\n• adapter_name (string): Unique ID, MUST match ConceptMap\n  适配器名称：必须与ConceptMap中一致\n• strength_model (float, default=1.0): LoRA strength for UNet\n  UNet的LoRA强度\n• strength_clip (float, default=1.0): LoRA strength for text encoder\n  文本编码器的LoRA强度\n\n## 2. Concept Map / 概念映射\n• concept_text: Description text for this concept\n  MUST appear verbatim in prompt\n  概念文本：必须原样出现在提示词中\n• enable_background (bool, default=true): Background as separate concept\n  将背景作为独立概念处理\n• background_text (string): Background description (optional)\n  背景描述（可选，留空则自动检测）\n\n## 3. Token Positions / Token位置\n• filter_meaningless (bool, default=true): Remove articles/prepositions\n  过滤冠词/介词等无意义词\n• filter_single_char (bool, default=true): Remove single-char tokens\n  过滤单字符token\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 4. Phase 1 Sampler / 阶段1采样器\n\n### Core Parameters / 核心参数\n• steps (int, default=30): Total steps, MUST match Phase 2\n  总步数：须与阶段2一致\n• collect_step (int, default=10): Collect attention then early-stop\n  收集注意力后提前终止的步骤（SDXL推荐10）\n• cfg (float, default=7.0): Standard CFG guidance scale\n  标准CFG引导尺度（SDXL推荐7.0）\n• sampler_name: euler recommended for SDXL\n  SDXL推荐euler\n• scheduler: normal recommended for SDXL\n  SDXL推荐normal\n\n### Block Selection [SDXL] / Block选择\n• collect_region (enum): UNet region to collect attention\n  收集注意力的UNet区域\n  ★ output_early recommended / 推荐output_early\n• collect_tf_index (int, default=3): Transformer index in region (0-9)\n  该区域内的transformer索引（0-9）\n• collect_block: [Flux only, ignored for SDXL]\n  [仅Flux，SDXL忽略此参数]\n\n### Similarity / 相似度计算\n• temperature (float, default=0→auto:300):\n  Softmax temperature. Higher = sharper maps\n  Softmax温度，越高→越锐利的映射（SDXL自动值300）\n• top_k_ratio (float, default=0.1):\n  Ratio of top-k tokens for similarity\n  top-k token比例\n\n### LoRA Control / LoRA控制\n• disable_lora_phase1 (bool, default=true ★):\n  Disable LoRA for cleaner base-model attention\n  禁用LoRA以获取更干净的注意力 ★推荐\n\n### Mask Post-processing / 掩码后处理\n• bg_scale (float, default=0.95):\n  Background scaling. Higher = more background\n  背景缩放，越高→背景越大\n• use_morphological_cleaning (bool, default=false):\n  Clean mask boundaries with morphology\n  形态学清理掩码边界\n\n### Mask Balancing (Advanced) / 掩码平衡（高级）\n• balance_iterations (int, 15): Balanced argmax iterations\n  平衡argmax迭代次数\n• balance_lr (float, 0.01): Bias update learning rate\n  偏置更新学习率\n• gravity_weight (float, 0.01): Centroid attraction\n  质心吸引力（SDXL推荐0.01，比Flux大）\n• spatial_weight (float, 0.00004): Neighbor voting\n  邻域投票（空间平滑性）\n• momentum (float, 0.2): Smoothing between iters\n  迭代间平滑动量\n• centroid_margin (float, 0.0): Clamp from borders\n  质心边界夹紧\n• border_penalty (float, 0.0): Border assignment penalty\n  边界分配惩罚\n• anisotropy (float, 1.3): H-stretch >1=wider masks\n  各向异性 >1=更宽的掩码\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 5. Mask Applicator / 掩码应用器\n\n### LoRA Masking / LoRA掩码\n• enable_token_masking (bool, true):\n  Zero LoRA at other concepts' tokens\n  在其他概念token处清零LoRA输出\n\n### Attention Bias / 注意力偏置\n• enable_attention_bias (bool, true):\n  Apply attention bias to guide cross-attention\n  启用注意力偏置引导交叉注意力\n• bias_scale (float, 5.0): Negative bias strength\n  Suppress cross-LoRA attention (5-10 typical)\n  负偏置强度（抑制跨LoRA注意力，典型值5-10）\n• positive_bias_scale (float, 7.0):\n  Enhance same-LoRA attention (SDXL uses higher value)\n  正偏置强度（SDXL使用较高值7.0）\n• bidirectional: [Flux only, ignored for SDXL]\n  [仅Flux，SDXL交叉注意力本身是单向的]\n• use_positive_bias (bool, true):\n  Add positive bias for matched pairs\n  为匹配对添加正偏置\n• bias_blocks: Which blocks get bias\n  应用偏置的block范围\n  ★ all recommended for SDXL / SDXL推荐all\n  - all: All blocks / 所有block\n  - none: Disable / 禁用\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 6. KSampler (Phase 2)\n• seed: Same as Phase 1 / 与阶段1相同\n• steps: MUST match Phase 1 (30) / 须一致\n• cfg: 7.0 recommended for SDXL / SDXL推荐7.0\n• sampler/scheduler: Match Phase 1 / 与阶段1一致\n• denoise: 1.0 for full generation / 完整生成\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## SDXL vs Flux Key Differences / SDXL与Flux主要区别\n• CFG: SDXL uses standard CFG (7.0) / SDXL用标准CFG\n  Flux uses guidance embedding (cfg=1.0)\n• Negative prompt: SDXL supported ✓ / SDXL支持 ✓\n  Flux not supported ✗\n• collect_step: SDXL=10, Flux=5\n• temperature auto: SDXL=300, Flux=4000\n• gravity_weight: SDXL=0.01, Flux=0.00004\n• positive_bias_scale: SDXL=7.0, Flux=1.0\n• bias_blocks: SDXL=all, Flux=double_stream_only\n• Text encoder: SDXL=CLIPTextEncode\n  Flux=CLIPTextEncodeFlux"
